title: Kiss Person Woman Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Depicts a loving kiss between a woman with a medium-dark skin tone and a man with a default, non-specified skin tone. It symbolizes romantic love, passion, and connection.
apple_vendor_description: The kiss emoji on Apple devices portrays a woman with a medium-dark skin tone, her face angled slightly as if in mid-embrace, her lips pursed gently. Apple’s distinctive glossy 3D shading adds a touch of realism, with soft highlights suggesting a tender moment. The smooth gradients and rounded features contribute to an intimate and affectionate tone, making this emoji perfect for conveying romantic feelings or a sweet farewell in digital conversations on Apple devices.
